ğŸ”· Step 2: Create the Web App
bash
Copy
Edit
az webapp create \
  --resource-group myResourceGroup \
  --plan myAppPlan \
  --name mywebapp123 \
  --runtime "NODE|18-lts" \
  --deployment-local-git
âœ… This gives you a Git URL to push code to the App Service.

